    <item>
      <title>巴西11月失业率再次下降，表明劳动力市场具有弹性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/brazil-unemployment-falls-further-in-november</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西失业率连续第八个月下降，表明随着拉丁美洲最大经济体经济放缓，劳动力市场仍然保持坚挺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/brazil-unemployment-falls-further-in-november</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 12:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大皇家银行表示，美国经济仍有可能陷入衰退，股市反弹令股市脆弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/rbc-says-rally-makes-stocks-vulnerable-with-us-recession-still-likely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行基金管理部门表示，股市上涨如此之快，如果美国经济陷入轻微衰退，股市就很容易出现回调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-29/rbc-says-rally-makes-stocks-vulnerable-with-us-recession-still-likely</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
